{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e42d2b1bf5","title":"关于修改在庆祝五一劳动节大会上的讲话稿给刘少奇的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"04497e0d44","index":0,"year":1950,"month":4,"day":29,"articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"d20738c862","name":"世界形势","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"eb663a7b61","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这句口号是：全中国各民族各民主阶级各民主党派各人民团体的团结合作万岁！"}],"contents":[{"id":"ff89bb709c","type":"title","text":"关于修改在庆祝五一劳动节大会上的讲话稿给刘少奇的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"},{"id":"eb663a7b61","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"},{"id":"8f16ab9597","type":"paragraph","text":"报告略有些修改，已送恩来阅后还你。陈云在请假中不看文件，没有送他看。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"},{"id":"54bfc13436","type":"paragraph","text":"修改的主要点如下：不要说“今年是困难的最后一年”，因今后几年内都会有困难，而且仍将是相当严重的困难，不过将一年一年地减少黑了。其他说到困难“很快就可以过去”的话都删掉了。举东北为例一段合并到前面一段中去。国际形势一段说得策略一些。解释富农策略一段觉累赞，留待将来去说。纠正命令主义一段说得全面一些，并且不要太突出地去说财经干部。口号加了一句”","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"},{"id":"79a4661af8","type":"paragraph","text":"如时间来得及，请于你讲后即刻付排，送清样给我再看一次，然后发表。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"},{"id":"8941f02e54","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"},{"id":"640099b2c1","type":"paragraph","text":"四月廿九日上午五时","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5"}],"page":{"id":"74ded06d17","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"e42d2b1bf5","start":321,"end":321}}}},"__N_SSG":true}